        <h2>corporate communications<br>& investor relations</h2>
        <hr/>
        <p class="mb-lg">accessible, standards-driven sustainability communications microsites focused on cross-device reliability.</p>
        <p class="mt-xs text-sm font-light color-faint">11ty · njk · md · SCSS · JS · node.js · Lighthouse · WCAG · Wave · Core Web Vitals · VS Code · git · Figma · Asana · Slack</p>
      </div>

      <div class="logos">
        <div class="columns columns-6">
          <div class="logo">
            <div class="logo__svg">{% svg "rtx.svg" %}</div>
          </div>

          <div class="logo">
            <div class="logo__svg"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="logo">
            <div class="logo__svg">{% svg "dominion-energy.svg" %}</div>
          </div>

          <div class="logo">
            <div class="logo__svg">{% svg "agco.svg" %}</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article>
      <div class="feature">
        <h2>education, health <br>& public impact</h2>
        <hr/>
        <p class="mb-lg">WordPress and static sites built for accessible editorial clarity and long-term maintainability.</p>
        <p class="mt-xs text-sm font-light color-faint">wordpress · jekyll · liquid · php · JS · node.js · Lighthouse · WCAG · Wave · Core Web Vitals · sublime text · git · sketch · trello · Slack</p>
