        <h2>media<br>& entertainment</h2>
        <hr/>
        <p class="mb-lg">large-scale media and entertainment platforms engineered for SEO visibility, Core Web Vitals performance, and high-volume audience reach.</p>
        <p class="mt-xs text-sm font-light color-faint">custom CMS · Jinja · mustache · css3 · jquery · a/b testing · Core Web Vitals · SEO audits · Aptana · git · Photoshop · Jira · wrike · winscp</p>
